                        Ausstellers</rs>, 2.<rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_luchner_QGW_II_I_619">
                        Niclas des Luchner, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">purger</roleName> ze Wienn</rs>.</rs>
